The test project already exists at `/tmp/sv-f392c6a8e58f4940a67dc53149514c9b/ContosoUniversity.Tests/ContosoUniversity.Tests.csproj` with references to the main project, Moq, and Microsoft.EntityFrameworkCore.InMemory.

## Key architecture details

All controllers inherit from BaseController:
```csharp
public abstract class BaseController : Controller
{
    protected SchoolContext db;
    protected NotificationService notificationService = new NotificationService();

    public BaseController(SchoolContext context) { db = context; }

    protected void SendEntityNotification(string entityType, string entityId, EntityOperation operation) { ... }
    protected void SendEntityNotification(string entityType, string entityId, string entityDisplayName, EntityOperation operation) { ... }

    protected override void Dispose(bool disposing) { ... }
}
```

SchoolContext (EF Core DbContext):
```csharp
public class SchoolContext : DbContext
{
    public SchoolContext(DbContextOptions<SchoolContext> options) : base(options) { }
    public DbSet<Course> Courses { get; set; }
    public DbSet<Enrollment> Enrollments { get; set; }
    public DbSet<Department> Departments { get; set; }
    public DbSet<OfficeAssignment> OfficeAssignments { get; set; }
    public DbSet<CourseAssignment> CourseAssignments { get; set; }
    public DbSet<Person> People { get; set; }
    public DbSet<Student> Students { get; set; }
    public DbSet<Instructor> Instructors { get; set; }
    public DbSet<Notification> Notifications { get; set; }
    // OnModelCreating configures TPH inheritance for Person, composite key for CourseAssignment, etc.
}
```

## Models

Person (abstract): ID, LastName, FirstMidName, FullName (computed)
Student extends Person: EnrollmentDate, Enrollments collection
Instructor extends Person: HireDate, CourseAssignments collection, OfficeAssignment
Course: CourseID (DatabaseGenerated.None), Title, Credits, DepartmentID, TeachingMaterialImagePath, Department nav, Enrollments, CourseAssignments
Department: DepartmentID, Name, Budget, StartDate, InstructorID?, RowVersion (Timestamp), Administrator nav, Courses
Enrollment: EnrollmentID, CourseID, StudentID, Grade?, Course nav, Student nav
CourseAssignment: composite key (InstructorID, CourseID), Instructor nav, Course nav
OfficeAssignment: Key=InstructorID, Location, Instructor nav
Notification: Id, EntityType, EntityId, Operation, Message, CreatedAt, CreatedBy, IsRead, ReadAt

